dct_title_s: Plano callejero de Bilbao-Bilbo con mapa provincial de Vizcaya-Bizkaia, escala plano 1:9.000, escala mapa 1:170.000 = Bilbao-Bilbo, roteiro/mapa de estradas = Bilbao-Bilbo street map/road map = Bilbao-Bilbo, Stadtplan/Landkarte = Bilbao-Bilbo, plan des rues/carte routière.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights on map of Bizkaia-Vizcaya. Depths shown by gradient tints. Cover title. On cover: RACE. "© Editorial Everest, S.A., Cartografía Everest ..." Includes ancillary map of "Bilbao/Bilbo" showing metropolitan area. Bizkaia-Vizcaya map shows international, interautónomico, interprovincial boundaries, index, and location of tourist services. Map of Bilbao the hotels are listed and located, includes and index.
